<h4>Overview</h4>
<p>
<b>Context:</b> the Editor supports taxonomy reviews, which precede publication of a new taxonomy;
<p>
<b>Draft:</b> the Editor allows you to draft a new taxonomy, based on an existing published taxonomy;
<p>
<b>Review:</b> the Editor lets you set up a taxonomy review, with a defined <b>review period</b> during which selected reviewers can <b>review</b>, and optionally...
<p>
<b>Comment</b> on the draft taxonomy, including reading other comments and responding to them;
<p>
<b>Review Periods:</b> can be added to a review to allow another cycle of review and comments, and this will let you...
<p>
<b>Repeat:</b> the draft-review-comment cycle with successive review periods until the review is complete, after which you will normally...
<p>
<b>Publish:</b> the reviewed taxonomy.
