<h4>Terminology</h4>
Within the Editor, successive publications of a taxonomy are referred to as <i><b>versions</b></i> of the taxonomy.  An unpublished taxonomy is a <b><i>draft</i> version</b> of the taxonomy.
<h4>Links on this tab</h4>
<p>
Links here generally lead to Editor queries, usually with detail tabs where you can drill into and edit records, including taxonomy review records.
<p>
You may find it helpful to keep multiple browser tabs open, perhaps to display this guide in one of them while you use the Editor interface on other browser tabs.
</p>
Everything you can add or edit on this page can also be done via the standard Editor interface.

